New Katia Magazines

   Discover more than 250 patterns of garments and complements for Ladies,
   Men, Children, Babies and Home.
   Find all the necessary material to make your projects on our online
   yarn shop.

   See All

Katia Fabrics

   Winter comes full of garments made from comfortable fabrics that feel
   like an embrace. This season we have added tricot, ideal for playing
   outdoors, to the existing fleece and soft jersey fabrics. To make sure
   that the kids don’t stop playing, even on the greyest of days, we have
   added a waterproof line with design pieces to make being out in the
   rain fun.

   See All

